  "texts": [
    "In terms of the results in this paper, we shall end by briefly commenting and speculating on three particular issues.",
    "JHEP04(2024)048Consequences of the global symmetry.",
    "In section 5.2, we argued that there is an exact global symmetry of the minimal tension string, corresponding to a shift in the zero mode of the radial coordinate of AdS 3.",
    "The radial translation global symmetry and the localisation to covering maps suggests that the theory has some level of background independence and is perhaps topological [3,24].",
    "Furthermore, the fact that the zero mode of Φ is not physical has consequences for the interpretation of the theory."
  ]
